**`*cn`* function should be used only in a case you are merging styles**:
className="mr-4 pb-6" GOOD
className={cn("mr-4 pb-6")} BAD

**“Base” styles should be declared first, overriding - last:**
className={cn("mr-4 pb-6", props.className)} GOOD
className={cn(props.className, "mr-4 pb-6" )} BAD

**Conditional classes should be declared this way:**
className={cn("mr-4 pb-6", {"border-5": isBorderVisible})} GOOD
className={cn(`mr-4 pb-6 ${isBorderVisible ? "border-5" : ""}` )} BAD